				<p>Thanks for the post, very nice.</p>
<p>Seriously though, Keyword Luv creates a symbiotic relationship.  The blogger gets more comments (and therefore, more visits), and the commenter gets a one-way backlink.</p>
<p>When I post, I make a point of (a)reading the post, (b)writing something appropriate and of value to the discussion, and (c)not mentioning my business unless it is germane to the subject.</p>
<p>I also hate when people put their link in the body of their &#8220;comment&#8221; too.  I mean, you already got a backlink, tied to your keyword and everything, so calm down.</p>
