			<div class="comment-content comment-text">
				
				
				<p>Have you considered using the dofollow trackbacks plugin? It seems more justified to me to reward those who link to you than those who comment. I&#8217;ve just installed it on my blog as a test.</p>
<p>Of course, it can be spammed just as much, but having to link to a post to gain a link should deter most spammers, and Akismet will catch the auto-generated sites.</p>
